                <div class="rendering rendering_researchoutput  rendering_researchoutput_apa rendering_contributiontojournal rendering_apa rendering_contributiontojournal_apa">Leal, J., Murphy, J., Garriga, C., Delmestri, A., Rangan, A., Price, A., Carr, A., Prieto-Alhambra, D.<a rel="Person" href="https://research-information.bris.ac.uk/en/persons/andy-judge/" class="link"><span>, &amp; Judge, A.</span></a> (2020). <a rel="ContributionToJournal" href="https://research-information.bris.ac.uk/en/publications/costs-of-joint-replacement-in-osteoarthritis-a-study-using-the-na/" class="link"><span>Costs of joint replacement in osteoarthritis: a study using the National Joint Registry and Clinical Practice Research Datalink datasets</span></a>. <a rel="Journal" href="#" class="link"><span><em>Arthritis Care and Research</em></span></a>, <em>74</em>(3), 392-402. <a onclick="window.open(this.href, '_blank','noopener,noreferrer'); return false;" href="https://doi.org/10.1002/acr.24470" class="link"><span>https://doi.org/10.1002/acr.24470</span></a></div>
